1
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:38,719
Chief Zhao.

2
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,640
How is Ruolan doing?

3
00:01:41,519 --> 00:01:42,120
Ming Liang.

4
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:43,719
What are you doing here?

5
00:01:44,799 --> 00:01:46,040
Let me go up and see Ruolan.

6
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,159
I'm really worried about her.

7
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:48,519
Some other time.

8
00:01:49,159 --> 00:01:50,400
She doesn't want to see anyone right now.

9
00:01:51,319 --> 00:01:52,599
She locks herself in her room all day.

10
00:01:53,879 --> 00:01:55,840
Chief Zhao, just let me try.

11
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:57,159
Maybe she wants to talk to a friend.

12
00:01:57,159 --> 00:01:58,560
Can you stop making things worse?

13
00:01:58,959 --> 00:02:00,519
Don't you know what she just went through?

14
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:04,439
In her state, why would she see anyone?

15
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:06,680
Especially a man.

16
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:07,719
Then...

17
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,479
I'll come back another day.

18
00:02:10,599 --> 00:02:12,680
Chief Zhao, if you need anything,

19
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,599
just call me anytime.

20
00:02:13,599 --> 00:02:14,759
My phone's on 24/7.

21
00:02:24,199 --> 00:02:24,960
Ruolan.

22
00:02:25,919 --> 00:02:27,039
Please get better soon.

23
00:02:28,719 --> 00:02:31,159
Then I'll treat you to a seafood feast.

24
00:03:10,719 --> 00:03:11,560
Thanks, driver.

25
00:03:26,479 --> 00:03:28,080
Ruolan, this place is so remote.

26
00:03:28,719 --> 00:03:30,080
It's not very accessible either.

27
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,280
It's not that bad.

28
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,479
Why don't you just move back home?

29
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:36,080
You've taken care of me my whole life.

30
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,960
I need to learn to be independent too.

31
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,360
My coworker Lili rented this place.

32
00:03:41,479 --> 00:03:42,840
It may just be a one-story house,

33
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:45,159
but it's really close to where I work.

34
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:47,599
And taking the bus is really easy.

35
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,719
Best of all, we split the rent.

36
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,840
I can save quite a bit of money.

37
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,360
Save, save, save.

38
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,360
That's all you think about.

39
00:03:55,159 --> 00:03:56,360
I make enough to support you.

40
00:03:57,800 --> 00:04:00,319
Bro, you're still single.

41
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,759
Shouldn't you save up for a wife?

42
00:04:05,639 --> 00:04:06,439
Not anytime soon.

43
00:04:07,039 --> 00:04:08,319
I can barely keep up with my cases.

44
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:11,199
Forgot what Mom told you before she passed?

45
00:04:11,439 --> 00:04:13,680
Okay, okay, I'll listen to you.

46
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,879
I'll start looking for a wife tomorrow.

47
00:04:15,879 --> 00:04:16,879
Now that's more like it.

48
00:04:17,879 --> 00:04:18,879
I only have one requirement.

49
00:04:19,639 --> 00:04:20,720
She has to know how to cook.

50
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:23,279
You little glutton.

51
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,680
Tormenting yourself like this,

52
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,079
is that gonna help you catch the bastard?

53
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,439
After all these days,

54
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,680
we haven't found a trace of Red Gloves.

55
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:23,279
We haven't found Ruolan's crime scene.

56
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:31,920
I'm so useless.

57
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:33,720
I don't deserve to be Ruolan's brother,

58
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:36,160
let alone lead the Major Crimes Unit.

59
00:05:36,959 --> 00:05:37,920
It's not your fault.

60
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,920
It is my fault.

61
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,199
If I hadn't let her come here,

62
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,360
none of this would've happened.

63
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,040
Captain,

64
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,920
what's done is done.

65
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:52,519
Guilt won't change anything.

66
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,040
It'll only hinder the investigation.

67
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:57,160
Every day you stay down like this,

68
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,439
there could be another victim.

69
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:02,759
Right?

70
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,160
You're right.

71
00:06:16,759 --> 00:06:20,079
I'll bring that monster to justice myself.

72
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:26,680
Yeah?

73
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,519
Okay, got it.

74
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:32,639
We got a lead.

75
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:47,000
Didn't I tell you to rest a few more days?

76
00:06:48,079 --> 00:06:48,800
I'm already fine.

77
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,000
The thing is, I can't just lie around.

78
00:06:50,639 --> 00:06:52,399
From footprints at the struggle scene,

79
00:06:52,399 --> 00:06:53,759
we extracted the same substance.

80
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,040
It's being analyzed now.

81
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,000
Sister Fei,

82
00:06:57,519 --> 00:06:58,920
are these Ruolan's clothes?

83
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,240
Jiang Han.

84
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:04,240
Yes, sir.

85
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:05,399
Ruolan's case

86
00:07:05,399 --> 00:07:07,399
is no different from the other victims'.

87
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:08,800
I'm the captain.

88
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,759
Forget that I'm Ruolan's brother.

89
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:13,800
Yes, Captain Zhao.

90
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:14,439
Go on.

91
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,319
Aren't these clothes a bit too intact?

92
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,839
Not a single button is missing.

93
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,720
Based on previous cases,

94
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:25,839
the victims' clothes are usually shredded.

95
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:29,839
Continue.

96
00:07:31,319 --> 00:07:33,240
I think Red Gloves was very patient.

97
00:07:33,839 --> 00:07:35,120
He didn't carve anything on Ruolan.

98
00:07:35,759 --> 00:07:37,199
Is there a special reason for that?

99
00:07:38,879 --> 00:07:39,959
Jiang Han has a point.

100
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:43,519
This is different from previous cases.

101
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:47,199
From a biological standpoint,

102
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,839
gentle actions

103
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:51,600
respect the partner's feelings and body.

104
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,839
It's an expression of love and care.

105
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,639
But this case is different.

106
00:07:56,959 --> 00:07:59,439
The suspect has abnormal preferences.

107
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,959
The gentle way he unbuttoned the clothes

108
00:08:02,959 --> 00:08:04,560
is a way for him to achieve sexual arousal

109
00:08:05,519 --> 00:08:06,959
or psychological satisfaction.

110
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:09,040
Such a drastically different MO

111
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,879
indicates the suspect

112
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:13,079
has a severe split personality.

113
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,000
The report's in.

114
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,600
It has high molecular weight hydrocarbons

115
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,800
and a mixture of non-hydrocarbons.

116
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:23,959
Petroleum.

117
00:08:24,639 --> 00:08:26,240
Could also be motor oil.

118
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,120
That fight of yours wasn't for nothing.

119
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,319
You've earned a major commendation.

120
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:31,959
Hey, Boss.

121
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:06,600
Boss.

122
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:09,360
I've checked most suburban auto shops.

123
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:11,159
This is the last one left.

124
00:09:12,039 --> 00:09:14,200
The main entrance is sealed off.

125
00:09:14,679 --> 00:09:15,799
There's a side door here.

126
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,759
It's been abandoned for over a year.

127
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,679
Why are there so many tire tracks here?

128
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,120
These tire tracks

129
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,519
have different patterns

130
00:09:43,799 --> 00:09:44,720
and varying depths,

131
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:48,360
meaning different vehicles passed by.

132
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:52,200
This road leads north to the city,

133
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,960
and south to the national highway.

134
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:55,960
Before Ping'an Avenue was built,

135
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,879
a lot of vehicles would stop here.

136
00:09:59,919 --> 00:10:01,919
Two years ago, Ping'an Avenue opened,

137
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,879
and fewer cars came through here.

138
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,799
This auto shop must have lost business

139
00:10:05,919 --> 00:10:06,799
and shut down.

140
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,919
That's why this could be the crime scene.

141
00:10:12,679 --> 00:10:13,919
Few vehicles pass through here,

142
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,159
making it easy to commit a crime.

143
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:17,039
That's why we didn't catch him that night.

144
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:24,799
You guys wait here.

145
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:25,639
You, come with me.

146
00:10:25,639 --> 00:10:26,519
Put your gloves on.

147
00:10:26,639 --> 00:10:27,159
Okay.

148
00:10:36,759 --> 00:10:37,519
Watch where you step.

149
00:10:37,799 --> 00:10:38,519
Follow me.

150
00:10:51,559 --> 00:10:52,240
Who's there?

151
00:10:53,919 --> 00:10:55,039
What are you so nervous about?

152
00:10:56,639 --> 00:10:58,080
Nerves will cloud your judgment.

153
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:00,679
I get it.

154
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:02,200
It won't happen again.

155
00:11:48,759 --> 00:11:49,440
Boss!

156
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:13,720
Boss!

157
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:15,759
Don't move!

158
00:13:43,159 --> 00:13:44,960
This is where Ruolan was assaulted.

159
00:14:05,679 --> 00:14:06,720
Hey, Captain Zhao.

160
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:08,519
The forensic report is in.

161
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:13,200
The liquid in the syringe is a stimulant.

162
00:14:13,840 --> 00:14:14,480
Any fingerprints?

163
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:16,480
Yes, we're running them in the database.

164
00:14:34,759 --> 00:14:37,320
A match, Captain Zhao, it's a match!

165
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:42,919
Ma Shijiang, 26 years old.

166
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:45,200
Sentenced three years ago for assault.

167
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:47,200
Released from prison two months ago.

168
00:14:50,399 --> 00:14:52,120
Boss, Boss.

169
00:14:54,159 --> 00:14:54,799
Chief Xing.

170
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:56,159
What's going on?

171
00:14:57,159 --> 00:14:58,360
The serial rapist,

172
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,080
the killer of Liu Xiang,

173
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:01,200
and Ruolan's attacker must be Ma Shijiang.

174
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:03,960
Captain Zhao put him away back then.

175
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:05,720
So the attack on Ruolan

176
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:08,039
was likely a premeditated act of revenge.

177
00:15:29,639 --> 00:15:30,480
What's your name?

178
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:32,039
Don't recognize me?

179
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:33,480
Your grandpa here.

180
00:15:33,679 --> 00:15:35,279
The Tyrant of Fengdu, Ma Shijiang.

181
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:36,639
Cuff him.

182
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:37,840
You okay?

183
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:39,039
Move.

184
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:41,919
Zhao Qingming, you just wait!

185
00:15:42,559 --> 00:15:44,000
I'll get my revenge on you one day.

186
00:15:52,639 --> 00:15:53,279
Mom.

187
00:16:02,360 --> 00:16:03,799
I failed Ruolan.

188
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:05,759
Today's arrest operation

189
00:16:05,919 --> 00:16:07,399
will be commanded by Li Kaiyang.

190
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:11,159
Chief Xing.

191
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:13,399
Qingming.

192
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:15,639
Given your family ties to the victim,

193
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:17,000
you need to recuse yourself.

194
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:18,000
Chief Xing,

195
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:20,360
tonight is what I've been waiting for.

196
00:16:21,399 --> 00:16:23,799
I have to cuff that bastard myself.

197
00:16:24,159 --> 00:16:25,080
Leave it to Li Kaiyang.

198
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:26,080
Nothing will go wrong.

199
00:16:26,720 --> 00:16:27,399
No way.

200
00:16:27,919 --> 00:16:29,440
I have to join tonight's operation.

201
00:16:29,639 --> 00:16:30,240
Qingming.

202
00:16:32,879 --> 00:16:33,759
Zhao Qingming!

203
00:16:34,519 --> 00:16:35,039
Chief Gao.

204
00:16:35,039 --> 00:16:36,720
You're a veteran of the force.

205
00:16:37,679 --> 00:16:40,000
Are you really clueless, or just faking?

206
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:43,279
We all understand how you feel.

207
00:16:43,759 --> 00:16:45,200
Don't forget you're the captain.

208
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:48,080
Shouldn't you be more principled?

209
00:16:49,039 --> 00:16:49,639
Chief Gao,

210
00:16:50,399 --> 00:16:51,120
I understand.

211
00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:56,320
You've all worked hard lately.

212
00:16:57,519 --> 00:17:00,039
But tonight's arrest operation is crucial.

213
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:03,360
It's not just about justice under the law,

214
00:17:03,720 --> 00:17:06,920
but the public's safety and property,

215
00:17:07,079 --> 00:17:08,240
and social stability.

216
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:10,279
But I have faith in you.

217
00:17:10,640 --> 00:17:12,400
Because you're all the elite of the force.

218
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:15,720
You'll bring that suspect back to me.

219
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:18,519
Move out.

220
00:17:21,359 --> 00:17:22,279
One more thing.

221
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:25,160
Stick strictly to the operational rules.

222
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:27,160
Keep your team members safe.

223
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:28,119
Yes, sir!
